      "title": "SSP Ruwan appointed Police Legal Director",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Attorney-at-Law SSP Ruwan Gunasekara has been appointed as the Director of the Police Legal Division.",
        "The Police Media Division announced that the appointment was made by the Inspector General of Police subject to the approval of the Public Security Ministry Secretary.",
        "SSP Ruwan Gunasekara previously held the position of Director of Judicial Security Division.",
        "SLPP tells President to appoint State Ministers, if All-Party Govt. is further delayed"
      ],
